

tidy2spatial 0.0.1
----------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURES

* New function union_polygons: create a new SpatialPolygonsDataFrame with
  'unioned' polygons, starting from a SpatialPolygonsDataFrame
* Moved the maptools package from Imports to Depends
* New function union_tidy: combine tidy2sp, union_polygons and broom::tidy
* Added argument .keep_all = TRUE in a call to dplyr::distinct_ in function
  union_polygons, to be compatible with dplyr version 0.5.0.



tidy2spatial 0.0.0
----------------------------------------------------------------

NEW FEATURES

* Very first version of the package. Type help(package="tidy2spatial") to run documentation.
* Function tidy2sp: transforms a tidy data with map coordinates in a SpatialPolygonsDataFrame
